<div class="page">
<%= render 'layouts/header' %>


<h2>Edit Your Information</h2>

<%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name), html: { method: :put, :multipart => true }) do |f| %>
  <%= devise_error_messages! %>

  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :first_name %> 
    <%= f.text_field :first_name, autofocus: true %>
    <%= f.label :last_name %>
    <%= f.text_field :last_name, autofocus: true %>
  </div>
<br>
  <% if devise_mapping.confirmable? && resource.pending_reconfirmation? %>
    <div>Currently waiting confirmation for: <%= resource.unconfirmed_email %></div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :password %> <i>(leave this line and the confirmation blank unless you want to change your password)</i><br />
    <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off" %>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :password_confirmation %><br />
    <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off" %>
  </div>
<br>
<br>
  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :current_password %> <i>(you have to be authenticated (signed in) to make any changes to this page)</i><br />
    <%= f.password_field :current_password, autocomplete: "off" %>
  </div>
<br>
  <div>
  <h3>Add or replace your profile picture</h3>        

  
        <%= f.file_field :avatar, class: "btn btn-success" %>
        <%#= f.hidden_field :avatar_cache %>
      
   </div>    

  <div class="actions"><br>
    <%= f.submit "Save photo", class: 'btn btn-success' %>
  </div>
<% end %>
<br>
<%= link_to '<<Back', posts_path %>
<br><br>

<h3> Tell your story</h3>
<p>Don't let your fellow parishioners learn at your funeral that they had something in common with you! <em>(Is there a more delicate way to put this?)</em></p>
<p>Click here for  a questionnaire, of sorts, that you can use to introduce your deeper self. You can edit your profile from time to time as you wish. <%= link_to 'Take me there', new_profile_path, class: 'btn btn-success' %></p>

<br><br>
<hr>
<h3>Cancel this account</h3>

<p>Leaving the St. Paul's community? <%= link_to "Cancel my account", registration_path(resource_name), class: 'btn btn-danger', data: { confirm: "Are you sure? This will destroy all of your information, including posts, photos and comments." }, method: :delete %></p>

